{artist: Nickelback}
{title: Photograph}

Tabbed by: Mikael Thunborg
 
If you have any questions of opinions just email me on: moixe10@hotmail.com 
 
First thing you must do is to down tune you guitar a half step.
 
The tuning of this song is | D# G# C# F# A# D# |
 
then the chords are power chords but you play on all the strings and you must let
all the strings ring out clearly.
 
for example: when you play the first chords wich is an E you play on ALL the 
strings
when you hold down the power chord and you let the other strings that are open 
ring out!
I hope you understand how I mean :)
 
and just listen to song for the strumming pattern.
 
well well, here's the chords:
 
